subject: Golf
Solheim Cup (Golf)
lead_paragraph: Juli Inkster, 51, the wily Solheim Cup veteran, and Ryann O'Toole, 24, the wide-eyed first-timer, share more than a place on the U.S. team that will compete in the Solheim Cup this week in Ireland.
